    <item>
      <title>库存数据和伊朗制裁成为焦点，油价保持上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于行业报告显示美国原油库存减少，且交易员追踪对伊朗实施新制裁的进展，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 23:27:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉提振美国科技巨头，亚洲股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国科技巨头股价上涨后，亚洲股市预计将高开，华尔街投资者将其高风险收益视为股市牛市的重大考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国石油买家将承受美国对伊朗更严厉的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-oil-buyers-set-to-weather-tighter-us-sanctions-on-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的私营炼油厂可能会寻求购买更多来源不明的货物，以准备应对美国对伊朗出口的新制裁，以确保原油继续流向世界最大进口国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-oil-buyers-set-to-weather-tighter-us-sanctions-on-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Fortescue 铁矿石出货量因脱轨和天气下降 6%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/fortescue-s-iron-ore-shipments-fall-6-on-derailment-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球第四大铁矿石生产商Fortescue Ltd.表示，2024年前三个月炼钢材料出货量同比下降6%，反映出去年底矿车脱轨以及天气干扰的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/fortescue-s-iron-ore-shipments-fall-6-on-derailment-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:45:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金创纪录的上涨可能源于中国的狂热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/gold-s-record-setting-rally-may-have-its-roots-in-chinese-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金今年创纪录的涨幅令市场观察人士感到困惑，因为尽管存在本应抑制金价的逆风，但金价仍在飙升。随着本周价格下跌，原因可能在于中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/gold-s-record-setting-rally-may-have-its-roots-in-chinese-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼盾暴跌可能导致印尼央行在 2025 年之前无法降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/rupiah-slump-may-keep-bank-indonesia-rate-cuts-at-bay-until-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚央行可能会将货币宽松政策推迟到今年晚些时候，甚至是 2025 年初，因为它正在等待美联储利率路径的不确定性和中东持续的战斗结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/rupiah-slump-may-keep-bank-indonesia-rate-cuts-at-bay-until-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的审查引发企业坚持派息以转向股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-scrutiny-sparks-corporate-holdouts-to-hand-out-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国企业越来越多地提高股息支付，这表明监管推动提高股东回报正在取得成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-scrutiny-sparks-corporate-holdouts-to-hand-out-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小牛的鲁弗洛警告特鲁多加税后资本外逃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/maverix-s-ruffolo-warns-trudeau-of-capital-flight-after-tax-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位加拿大著名科技投资者加入了加拿大企业的行列，批评总理贾斯汀·特鲁多提高资本利得税的决定，认为这将导致资本外逃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/maverix-s-ruffolo-warns-trudeau-of-capital-flight-after-tax-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 21:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
